FT_LS:

>Test:
	-ft_ls [correct file] (v)
	-ft_ls [error file] (v)
	-ft_ls [correct file] [correct file] (v)
	-ft_ls [correct file] [error file] (v)
	-ft_ls [error file] [correct file] (v)
	-ft_ls [correct dir] [correct dir] (x)
		\_output format *
	-ft_ls [correct dir] [error dir] (x)
		\_output format *
	-ft_ls -R (x)
		\_output format *
	-ft_ls -R [correct dir] [correct dir] (x)
		\_output format *

* Output format:
	- when ac >= 2 => print dir name + space between **
		ex:	->./ft_ls . ..
			->.:
			->[file]
			->...
			->...
			->(space **)
			->..:
			->[file]
			->...
			->...
			->...
	- when ac == 1 => no dir name
